    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Next Sunday afternoon delegates\nfrom the local unions will meet for\nthe purpose of organizing a CEN\ntrail labor body which will be rep\nresentative in character. The\nmovement was inaugurated about\nthree months ago by the printing\ntrades and has met with the ap-\nprevail of very large majority Of\nthe Spokane unions so much so\nthat there appears to be no doubt\nbut that the new central body will\nbe a go from the start.\n\n\n1t is proposed to have a charter\nfrom the American Federation of\nLabor and all unions eligible to af-\nfiliate in such a body have been\nasked to send delegates."
    }
  ]
